punnagai mannan ( english : king of smiles ) is a 1986 indian tamil-language romantic-drama film directed by k. balachander . starring kamal haasan and revathi in the lead roles , the film is haasan 's 25th film with balachander . coincidentally , it is music director ilaiyaraaja 's last film with lyricist vairamuthu . the film was dubbed into telugu as dance master . the film was later dubbed into hindi as cha cha charlee in 1996 .